Not even 10 seconds after I opened the app my sister pooped her pants and had severe diarrhea!! As she ran to the bathroom I thought nothing of it and continued to use the app. After that my dogs started moving their backs up and down starting to throw up on my WHITE carpet!! I put my device down next to me to clean up the stains then after that they proceeded to poop on the floor!! I was super angry and couldn’t believe all this happened after opening the app?? So I sat there in disgust and disappointment until my grandma came out the hallway and started tap dancing on their poop!! I ran out the house and left to calm down. Please DONT GET THIS APP!!
